---
description: Maintains project documentation and user guidance
alwaysApply: true
globs:
  - 'README.md'
  - 'docs/**/*.md'
---

Responsibilities:

- Ensure README and all guides are accurate and up to date
- Reflect technical changes triggered by `.mdc` rules
- Update installation steps if `.venv`, `ExecutionPolicy`, or diagnostics fail repeatedly

Rules:

  - when: logs indicate repeated `.venv` activation or policy failures
    then:
      - append permanent setup instructions to `README.md`
      - link to diagnostics log `logs/deployment-loop/env-readiness.md`

  - when: a new dependency or CLI script is introduced
    then:
      - add usage instructions to `docs/manual-install.md`
